data.title: Brooke Maatz, DNP, APRN, CNP
data.meta_description: Brooke Maatz, DNP, APRN, CNP practices in Internal Medicine at Sanford Grand Forks Clinic in Grand Forks, ND
data.text:
A Nurse Practitioner in Internal Medicine

Brooke Maatz provides primary health care to individuals, families, groups of individuals and communities throughout their lifespan - including adults and elderly populations. She specializes in internal medicine.

She treats chronic conditions including:

Anxiety

Depression

High blood pressure and cholesterol

Type II diabetes

Brooke is also a community leader in the following:

Preceptor for nurse practitioner students

Advanced practice provider council member

Speaks: English

Specialties

Internal Medicine

Real Experiences from Real Patients

You trust recommendations from real people. That's why we provide comments and star ratings from patients who answer our surveys after their visits to Sanford Health. Star ratings are based on a 0-100 point scale converted to 1-5 stars. Providers must have a minimum of 30 patient ratings to receive a formal rating.
